  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Prerequisite Feat</strong></span><strong> - @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-feats.Br6Al8eXrEPiw3Ka]{Hand Crossbow Specialist}</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>This compartment holds a number of bolts, based on quality, and doubles as a holster for one hand crossbow. While this item is equipped to a hand crossbow, the user does not need to manually reload bolts after firing. The compartment will automatically reload a bolt after each shot until the compartment is empty.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The compartment jams on an attack roll of 1. The compartment will not reload until the jam is cleared. Clearing a jam requires a bonus action.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>It takes 1 minute to completely refill the compartment with a fresh set of bolts.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Creating the item:</strong></span></p>\n<p><strong>20 bolt compartment</strong> - You can craft this item with 4 hours of work and 25gp worth of components.</p>\n<p><strong>30 bolt compartment</strong> - You can craft this item with 8 hours of work and 150gp worth of components.</p>\n<p><strong>40 bolt compartment</strong> - You can craft this item with 1 fortnight of work and 1500gp worth of components.</p>",
